{"id":1156243008,"question_id":279,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"4 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1706164685,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"30 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1156243008/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Perfect Squares","memory":"43.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int numSquares(int n) {\n        int[] dp = new int[n+1];\n        dp[1] = 1;\n        \n        for(int i=1; i<=n; i++){\n            dp[i] = i; // add by one\n            for(int j=1; j*j<=i; j++){\n                dp[i] = Math.min(dp[i], dp[i-j*j]+1);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return dp[n];\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"perfect-squares","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
